首頁> 專業服務> 策略及新興市場成為領導者絕非僥倖  分享	需要採取甚麼樣的行動，才能迅速的將您的事業從一個構想發展成一個實體公司，繼而成為市場主力?	安永瞭解如何推動企業的持續成長，因為我們已經引導數千家生氣蓬勃、雄心壯志的企業從創立到成為市場領袖。	我們的策略及新興市場服務網絡，致力於協助全球企業快速成長時須因應的獨特挑戰與不斷改變的需求。藉由我們全球機構的經驗、專業能力與資源為 貴公司提供服務，使 貴公司與眾不同。	安永的策略及新興市場服務專業人員擅長向企業提供輔導首次公開募股的服務。事實上，我們平均每天輔導一家企業上市。	我們的策略及新興市場服務團隊網絡遍及全球超過100個國家，無論貴公司規模大小，我們均能夠持續提供服務。不論您的企業擴展至全國或是全世界，我們將永遠陪伴在您身旁。家族企業慈善捐獻	我們的調查結果顯示了家族企業以什麼方式進行慈善捐獻、什麼因素驅動家族企業進行慈善捐獻及如何對家族企業慈善捐獻進行評估。 聯絡我們  審計營運長台灣臺北張嵐菁Kim Chang  電話: +886 2 2757 8888 ext 2317執業會計師台灣臺北王彥鈞 Ian Wang 電話: +886 2 2757 8888 ext 2361執業會計師台灣北區洪茂益 Mars Hong 電話: +886 3 427 5008 ext 211執業會計師台灣中區林鴻光 Hank Lin 電話: +886 4 2305 5500 ext 108  Leading through disruption 	How will organisations not just survive in the face of disruption, but thrive? Business leaders at Strategic Growth Forum China provide insights.  How do you give direction when the landscape is constantly shifting?  Is your business strategy fit for a digital world? Begin your Digital Maturity Check now.  Staying ahead of the disruption curve  Maintaining a culture of innovation  Opportunities on the digital horizon  Building blocks to thrive in a digital age  How young companies are tackling digital disruption  EY Entrepreneurial Winning Women™ Asia-Pacific 	The 15 winning women entrepreneurs connect with advisors, entrepreneurs and the insights they need to scale their businesses at our annual conference. Read conference highlights.  Strategic Growth Forum China 2016 	How are Asia’s leading businesses accelerating their growth? Read highlights (report / agenda recaps) to gain fascinating insights from business leaders, entrepreneurs and advisors. 	Our report reveals how women entrepreneurs in Asia-Pacific practise five key behaviours to help themselves successfully scale to become market leaders.  Meet Asia-Pacific’s future market leaders	The 24 EY Accelerating Entrepreneurs from Asia-Pacific were selected for their innovative technology-based products or services and ambition to accelerate growth internationally. Lear